{"tid":1350722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（19:30）【元屯天安全接送  車隊準備就緒】","createTime":"2019-07-22T13:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T15:26:38.000Z","uid":107060,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aea3b700e0a739c21daa02b6885e8e4e42ab012f","tid":1350722,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:34:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/396949433812753/posts/1249515531889468?s=100000581382690&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F396949433812753%2Fposts%2F1249515531889468%3Fs%3D100000581382690%26sfns%3Dmo&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHqjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=c17ec5d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/396949433812753/posts/1249515531889468?s=100000581382690&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tgN040Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtgN040Z.jpg&h=af0a76ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（19:30）【元屯天安全接送  車隊準備就緒】<br />\n<br />\n我們大部分車手已準備好，亦已經出車，暫時安排到17輛，每輛亦會有熱血手足跟車。在此先感謝仗義幫忙的朋友。<br />\n<br />\n若大家有家人或朋友收夜，擔心單獨回去屯門、元朗、天水圍等地區的話，請與泰辦元朗主任鄧文傑（6371 2807）聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n//（16:45）據悉，博愛醫院及屯門醫院有大量醫護學生進行實習，而護士學校及醫院並沒有安排早放，有學生需要當值至晚上9點至10點許才下班。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以把我們的安全接送車隊的聯絡發給他們，或不能提早下班的朋友，我們盡力提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n//（15:45）<br />\n<br />\n今日不斷收到各方消息及相片，指屯門、元朗、天水圍一帶均可能出現街頭廝殺或黑幫隨機襲擊途人的情況。<br />\n<br />\n我們的安全車隊，如大家有需要，請隨時與 6371 2807（鄧文傑）聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n敬請注意，各種緊急狀況亦有可能出現，等候安排時請先確保自己安全。//"},{"pid":"861fad952210bf84a8627c775cecc96c76cbb56f","tid":1350722,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42a4416b50bf5f9070e08dfb4f503b848170ea9","tid":1350722,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:35:42.000Z","msg":"Thank you"},{"pid":"e407e7aa1d874ff0ccf71e0511a1375afe3416ab","tid":1350722,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc02465a811bece7b23efb18a265a0f8d205c25","tid":1350722,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"推比屯元天返緊屋企既朋友睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1625bff3f192a309503c970cd9dcdbd823c53a49","tid":1350722,"uid":59522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:37:14.000Z","msg":"做埋巡兵都得"},{"pid":"01a6383be94c792754a62034edaec4cebf4ea561","tid":1350722,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:37:47.000Z","msg":"個城市變成咁 再有錢都冇用"},{"pid":"38f6f3b86c63e6e4f8082fa8eed47d14363552da","tid":1350722,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38897f8c5cad669b9b24821a19d8252da5c17cb6","tid":1350722,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56ab0fb04afc31de8a1577003c7e47c0cae6b9e","tid":1350722,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359fe1cebcc007bf8fe313eb756a5814c4e31d4e","tid":1350722,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca281068467a4997b65959494f6c5639133f60c","tid":1350722,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor